---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base>
  <header id="top" class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-5 pt-20 pb-16">
    <p class="text-accent font-medium text-sm tracking-wide uppercase mb-4">Omics analysis, on demand</p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-[1.05]">
      Bioinformatics analysis,<br />
      <span class="text-accent">delivered as a report.</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-6 text-lg sm:text-xl text-slate-600 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
      Per-omics pricing, fixed turnaround, reproducible pipelines. For biotechs and academic labs that need results — not a full-time hire.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a href="https://submit.omicsdesk.com/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-ink text-white px-5 py-3 rounded-md font-medium hover:bg-slate-800 transition">
        Submit your data
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      </a>
      <a href="/pricing/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white text-ink border border-slate-200 px-5 py-3 rounded-md font-medium hover:bg-slate-50 transition">
        See pricing
      </a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-5 py-14 border-t border-slate-100">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">What we do</h2>
    <div class="mt-6 grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl">
      <p class="prose-p">
        OmicsDesk turns your raw sequencing or mass-spec data into a decision-ready report. You send FASTQs, raw MS files, or count matrices and a sample sheet. You get back a QC report, full statistical results, publication-ready figures, and a branded PDF summary — usually within 7–10 business days.
      </p>
      <p class="prose-p">
        Every analysis is run on a versioned Snakemake pipeline with pinned conda environments. You receive the code alongside the results, so nothing is a black box.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="services" class="bg-slate-50 border-y border-slate-100">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-5 py-16">
      <div class="flex items-end justify-between flex-wrap gap-4 mb-8">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Services &amp; pricing</h2>
          <p class="prose-p mt-3 max-w-2xl">Flat fees. No surprises. Every analysis includes QC, figures, Excel results, a PDF report, and the pipeline code.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="/pricing/" class="text-accent font-medium hover:underline underline-offset-4 text-sm">
          Full pricing &amp; scopes →
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <thead class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-600">
            <tr>
              <th class="text-left font-medium px-5 py-3">Omics type</th>
              <th class="text-left font-medium px-5 py-3">Price</th>
              <th class="text-left font-medium px-5 py-3">Up to</th>
              <th class="text-left font-medium px-5 py-3">Turnaround</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-slate-100">
            <tr><td class="px-5 py-3 font-medium">RNA-seq (bulk)</td><td class="px-5 py-3 font-mono">€2,500</td><td class="px-5 py-3">24 samples</td><td class="px-5 py-3">7 business days</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-5 py-3 font-medium">scRNA-seq</td><td class="px-5 py-3 font-mono">€3,500</td><td class="px-5 py-3">16 libraries</td><td class="px-5 py-3">10 business days</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-5 py-3 font-medium">Proteomics</td><td class="px-5 py-3 font-mono">€3,000</td><td class="px-5 py-3">24 samples</td><td class="px-5 py-3">7 business days</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-5 py-3 font-medium">Phosphoproteomics</td><td class="px-5 py-3 font-mono">€3,500</td><td class="px-5 py-3">24 samples</td><td class="px-5 py-3">10 business days</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-5 py-3 font-medium">ChIP-seq</td><td class="px-5 py-3 font-mono">€2,500</td><td class="px-5 py-3">24 samples</td><td class="px-5 py-3">7 business days</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-5 py-3 font-medium">ATAC-seq</td><td class="px-5 py-3 font-mono">€2,500</td><td class="px-5 py-3">24 samples</td><td class="px-5 py-3">7 business days</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
        Prices in EUR. USD invoicing available on request. 15% academic discount for requests from <span class="font-mono text-slate-600">.edu</span> / <span class="font-mono text-slate-600">.ac.*</span> institutional emails (excluding rush).
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="how" class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-5 py-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">How it works</h2>
    <div class="mt-10 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
          <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-accent text-white text-sm font-semibold flex items-center justify-center">1</span>
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Intake &amp; NDA</h3>
          <span class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-mono">day 0</span>
        </div>
        <p class="prose-p text-sm">You fill a short intake form (organism, sample count, contrasts, data access). NDA signed before any data is shared. Quote and proposal back within 2 business days.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
          <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-accent text-white text-sm font-semibold flex items-center justify-center">2</span>
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Analysis &amp; QC</h3>
          <span class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-mono">days 1–7</span>
        </div>
        <p class="prose-p text-sm">Raw data is processed on a validated Snakemake pipeline. You receive a QC check-in after alignment so we can catch data-level issues early — before the clock runs out on downstream analysis.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
          <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-accent text-white text-sm font-semibold flex items-center justify-center">3</span>
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Report &amp; handoff</h3>
          <span class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-mono">day 7 or 10</span>
        </div>
        <p class="prose-p text-sm">Branded PDF report, Excel workbook with full statistical results, figures at 300 dpi, and the pipeline code. Raw data is deleted within 30 days of delivery.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-slate-50 border-y border-slate-100">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-5 py-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">What you get, every time</h2>
      <div class="mt-8 grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 max-w-4xl">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-slate-200 p-5">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-sm">QC report</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1">HTML + summary table</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-slate-200 p-5">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-sm">Full statistical results</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1">TSV + Excel workbook</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-slate-200 p-5">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-sm">Publication-ready figures</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1">PNG at 300 dpi</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-slate-200 p-5">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-sm">Branded PDF report</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1">Executive summary, methods, conclusions</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-slate-200 p-5">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-sm">Reproducible pipeline code</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1">Snakemake + conda, versioned</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-slate-200 p-5">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-sm">NDA by default</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1">Raw data deleted within 30 days</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-5 py-16">
    <div class="bg-ink text-white rounded-xl p-8 md:p-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center gap-6 justify-between">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold">See a real sample report</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-300 mt-2 max-w-2xl">Mouse heart scRNA-seq + Visium spatial transcriptomics (public dataset GSE308859, 30k cells, 4 timepoints). Same format every client receives: QC, UMAP, cell-type annotation, trajectory, spatial maps, narrative.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/sample_report_mouse_heart_scRNA.pdf" download class="inline-flex shrink-0 items-center gap-2 bg-accent hover:bg-accent-dark text-white px-5 py-3 rounded-md font-medium transition">
        Download sample (PDF, 2.4 MB)
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4M7 10l5 5 5-5M12 15V3"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-5 py-16 border-t border-slate-100">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">About</h2>
    <p class="prose-p mt-6 max-w-3xl">
      OmicsDesk is run by <span class="font-semibold text-ink">Alessandro De Santis</span>, a computational biologist and co-founder of SynMiR (Italian biotech developing synthetic miRNA cancer therapeutics). The target discovery pipeline at SynMiR is built on the same multi-omics integration approach offered here: transcriptomics, proteomics, phosphoproteomics, and mutation data combined into patient-specific signaling networks.
    </p>
    <p class="prose-p mt-4 max-w-3xl">
      OmicsDesk exists to make that capability available to labs and biotechs without an in-house bioinformatics hire.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section id="contact" class="bg-slate-50 border-y border-slate-100">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-5 py-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Get a quote</h2>
      <p class="prose-p mt-3 max-w-2xl">
        Upload your data and a short brief. The intake agent drafts an analysis plan and a fixed quote in about a minute on the next page, with a copy in your inbox.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-4xl">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-slate-200 p-6 flex flex-col justify-between">
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold">Submit your data</h4>
            <p class="prose-p mt-2 text-sm">Raw data files (FASTQ, RAW/mzML, count matrix — whatever your platform produces) + an optional metadata sheet + a short description of what you measured and what you want compared. We send back a plan and quote.</p>
            <ul class="prose-p mt-4 text-sm space-y-1.5 list-disc list-inside text-slate-600">
              <li>Omics type and sample count</li>
              <li>Species and genome build (if known)</li>
              <li>The biological contrast you want tested</li>
              <li>Any deadline you're working against</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <a href="https://submit.omicsdesk.com/" class="mt-5 inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-ink text-white px-5 py-3 rounded-md font-medium hover:bg-slate-800 transition self-start">
            Submit your data
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-slate-200 p-6 flex flex-col justify-between">
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold">Prefer to email or talk first?</h4>
            <p class="prose-p mt-2 text-sm">
              Reach out to <a class="text-accent font-medium underline-offset-4 hover:underline" href="mailto:hello@omicsdesk.com">hello@omicsdesk.com</a> if you want to discuss scope before uploading, ask about custom work, or book a quick call.
            </p>
          </div>
          <a href="mailto:hello@omicsdesk.com?subject=OmicsDesk%20%E2%80%94%20pre-submission%20question" class="mt-5 inline-flex items-center gap-2 border border-slate-300 text-ink px-5 py-3 rounded-md font-medium hover:bg-slate-100 transition self-start">
            Email us
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
